@startuml
participant User
participant Website
participant "Flask API" as FlaskAPI
participant APIFree

User -> Website: Submit travel preferences (destination, dates, interests)
activate Website

Website -> FlaskAPI: POST /generate (preferences)
activate FlaskAPI

FlaskAPI -> APIFree: Request itinerary + image (preferences)
activate APIFree

APIFree --> FlaskAPI: 200 OK (itinerary JSON, image URL/base64)
deactivate APIFree

FlaskAPI --> Website: 200 OK (itinerary, image)
deactivate FlaskAPI

Website -> User: Display generated itinerary and image
deactivate Website
@enduml